section.text:

  Chapter V of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act (
  21 U.S.C. 351 et seq.
) is amended by adding at the end the following:

subparagraph.text:
the criteria for determining whether a nonprescription sunscreen active ingredient or combination of nonprescription sunscreen active ingredients has been used to a material extent and for a material time, as described in 
                section 201(p)(2) of the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act (
                21 U.S.C. 321(p)(2)
              );
